            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>remaining sliced onion </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, remove the pan from the heat and add the<strong> spinach</strong> with a splash of <strong>water</strong></p><p>Return the pan to the heat and cook for 2-3 min or until the spinach has wilted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1623678022526-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1623678022526-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
