            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1623678036597-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tangy lime tofu</strong> with the <strong>sticky ginger rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Top with the <strong>zingy quick-pickled onion</strong> and sprinkle your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
